
1. The Node class is instantiated 4 times within NetworkSimulator.java as opposed to having a file for each node (node1.c, ..., node4.c)
2. Some methods and variables are made public and static in NetworkSimulator.java to allow the Node class to access them
3. A Makefile is provided

--------------------
To clean up
--------------------
make clean


--------------------
To compile
--------------------
make all


--------------------
To run
--------------------
java Project3
